text: The RPG-26 Aglen is a disposable anti-tank rocket launcher that was made by the Soviet Union. It entered service in 1985. It can shoot to about 250 meters. ==Information about the gun== * Calibre: 72.5 mm * Length: 770 mm * Weight: 2.9 kg * Range: effective combat, 250 m * Operating temperature: -50 to +50Â°C ==Other websites== Category:Weapons
